{"tid":2126730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲作者唔敢用真名 竟然用左Now工作既施嘉雯做筆名 出版界表示同情不過無能為力","createTime":"2020-07-27T04:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T06:17:30.000Z","uid":22556,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"49112f1fef1d71fad8fe423f26499e886ff90a2b","tid":2126730,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:21:49.000Z","msg":"俗語有云：「唔怕生壞命，最怕改錯名」。近日有本深藍陣營所寫《香港顏色密碼》新書推出，本書由《亞洲周刊》、零傳媒同明報出版社聯合出版。作者除咗有撐警嘅專欄作家屈穎妍、有「前白宮發言人」之稱前新聞統籌專員馮煒光等，竟然出現「施嘉雯」三字。國際關係學者沈旭暉喺Facebook開post，轉載曾經喺明報工作17年、現時係電視台Now工作施嘉雯嘅回應，更大嘆唔少人誤會佢朋友係作者、要同佢割席，所以想轉載當事人嘅回應，還其清白。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">施嘉雯稱曾向負責編輯《香港顏色密碼》嘅江迅查詢該書作者「施嘉雯」身份，江迅回覆稱有位資深傳媒人寫咗篇訪問、但又唔想用自己真名，所以用咗「施嘉雯」。<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n江迅話佢自己都唔知「施嘉雯」係乜嘢人，如果知，都會勸對方唔好用，仲話出版界唔會要求用化名嘅作者註明，對施嘉雯遭遇表示同情，但無能為力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200726/SIDFKKBOPSTYC74IOHHA2ZCYCY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200726%2FSIDFKKBOPSTYC74IOHHA2ZCYCY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qxwOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=3e4ccf7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200726%2FSIDFKKBOPSTYC74IOHHA2ZCYCY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=830c184f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200726/SIDFKKBOPSTYC74IOHHA2ZCYCY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"4bc082318e481fed630fb9ecbed08088b46674dc","tid":2126730,"uid":199893,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:25:42.000Z","msg":"會唔會有心玩